{/* Tech Stack Overview */}

My Technology Stack

Welcome to the tech stack overview. Here you'll find the technologies I've worked with and the projects I've applied them to. Let's dive in!

{/* Programming Languages */}

Programming Languages

  • Python: Experienced in building web applications, data analysis, and scripting.
  • JavaScript: Proficient in frontend development, including frameworks like React.
  • Java: Intermediate experience with JavaFX for desktop applications.
  • HTML/CSS: Advanced skills in web design and responsive layouts.
  • PHP: Proficient in server-side scripting for dynamic web pages.
  • SQL: Knowledgeable in working with relational databases and writing queries.
{/* Frameworks */}

Frameworks

  • Django: High-level Python web framework for rapid development.
  • React: Utilized for building dynamic user interfaces.
  • Flask: Used for developing web applications with Python.
  • Bootstrap CSS: Frontend framework for developing responsive and mobile-first websites.
  • Tailwind CSS: Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development.
{/* Libraries */}

Libraries

  • NLTK: Natural language processing library for Python.
  • SpaCy: Advanced library for NLP tasks in Python.
  • Framer Motion: Animation library for React.
{/* Tools and Technologies */}

Tools and Technologies

  • Git: Version control for collaborative projects.
  • Node.js: Proficient in server-side JavaScript development.
  • PostgreSQL: Experience with relational database management systems.
  • Heroku: Deployment platform for hosting web applications.
  • VS Code: Preferred code editor for development projects.
  • API: Protocols for software communication in various applications.
{/* Highlighted Projects */}

Highlighted Projects

Below are some of the key projects where I applied the technologies listed above:

{/* Project 1: Twin Cities Weather and Tourism */}

Twin Cities Weather and Tourism Web Application

Technologies: PHP, JavaScript, HTML, CSS

Description: A comprehensive web application that integrates maps and live weather forecasts to enhance tourist experiences.

View Live
{/* Project 2: UWE Chatbot */}

UWE Chatbot

Technologies: Python, SpaCy, NLTK, GPT-3.5

Description: An advanced chatbot for providing educational support, utilizing state-of-the-art NLP techniques.
